rows.label: qev085406_MSG0001
rows.name: Glad to see Aisha's home safe.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085406_MSG0002
rows.name: It's all because of you. Thank you all so much.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085406_MSG0003
rows.name: Just try and make sure she can't get out again, okay?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085406_MSG0004
rows.name: I'm afraid that's not really an option.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085406_MSG0005
rows.name: It's not?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085406_MSG0006
rows.name: Just as we have our missions, Aisha has hers.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085406_MSG0007
rows.name:
And that mission is a tough oneâ€”
to roam this great land of Mira, one piece at a time.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085406_MSG0008
rows.name: Wow. Is that how you collect your data?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085406_MSG0009
rows.name: Exactly.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085406_MSG0010
rows.name:
I need her in one piece for my research.
Past that, she's on her own.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085406_MSG0011
rows.name:
Oh please. If this was only about gathering data,
you could've just used FrontierNav.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085406_MSG0012
rows.name: Admit it. You were worried sick about her![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085406_MSG0013
rows.name: H-hey![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085406_MSG0014
rows.name: Meh-meh! There goes kitty cat![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085406_MSG0015
rows.name: Stay safe, little friend.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085406_MSG0016
rows.name: Freedom seems to suit her well.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085406_MSG0017
rows.name: I'm almost jealous.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085406_MSG0018
rows.name:
I look forward to the day I can run around
in my real body again. It's been so long.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085406_JNK0010
rows.name: Agree

rows.label: qev085406_SEL0011
rows.name: Smile and nod.

rows.label: qev085406_JNK0020
rows.name: Worry

rows.label: qev085406_SEL0021
rows.name: Wonder aloud if that day will ever come.

rows.label: qev085406_MSG0019
rows.name:
Although, you guys are in for quite a
shock when that day comes.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085406_MSG0020
rows.name: Huh? Why is that?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085406_MSG0021
rows.name: Hmm, why spoil the surprise?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085406_MSG0022
rows.name: Of course it will. We're gonna MAKE it come![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085406_MSG0023
rows.name: But until it does, we're on the clock. So let's get moving.[ST:wait ]
